parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt to retract into the holder can render the seat belt useless, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract into the holder
the seat belt remains loose and cannot be used
the seat belt is stuck in the retracted position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can prevent the seat belt from latching or unlatching, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle breaks or cracks
the seat belt buckle is hard to use or latch
the seat belt buckle comes loose occasionally
fragments of the buckle break off
rendering the seat belt inoperative.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt to lock into the buckle can prevent the seat belt from functioning properly, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to lock into the buckle
the seat belt is hard to latch or unlatch
the seat belt buckle is defective.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Failure to Repair/Replace Defective Seat Belts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to repair or replace defective seat belts in a timely manner can lead to continued use of faulty seat belts, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The manufacturer or dealer fails to repair or replace defective seat belts
the consumer is left with a faulty seat belt
the repair order is delayed or ignored.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's seat assembly can cause the seat to wobble, move unexpectedly, or even break loose, which can lead to accidents or injuries, especially during sudden maneuvers or in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The driver's seat wobbles
the seat moves up and down or back and forth
the seat feels unstable
the seat latch or bracket breaks
the seat slides or shifts unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the valve cover gasket can cause oil leaks, which can lead to engine damage, overheating, and potentially cause an accident.
symptoms: Oil leaks
coolant leaks
engine noise
decreased engine performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the coolant system can cause engine overheating, which can lead to engine damage, stalling, and potentially cause an accident.
symptoms: Coolant leaks
engine overheating
temperature gauge rising
engine stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of engine power can cause accidents, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power
engine stalling
difficulty accelerating
loss of engine performance.
